    <section>
      <h2>Why Jobsolv Wins</h2>

      <h3>1. Free Access to Core Features</h3>
      <p>AI Auto Apply requires payment to use. Jobsolv's free tier includes the job board, resume builder, job tracker, and limited resume tailoring. You can start applying immediately without a credit card.</p>
      <p><strong>User pain solved:</strong> Can't afford paid tools while job searching → <strong>Outcome:</strong> Start applying today at zero cost</p>

      <h3>2. Per-Job Resume Tailoring</h3>
      <p>AI Auto Apply uses one generic resume for all applications. Jobsolv tailors your resume for each job, matching keywords and skills from the job description. This significantly improves ATS pass rates and interview conversion.</p>
      <p><strong>User pain solved:</strong> Generic resumes get rejected by ATS → <strong>Outcome:</strong> Higher interview rates with targeted applications</p>

      <h3>3. Integrated Job Board</h3>
      <p>You don't need to browse external sites. Jobsolv's job board focuses on remote and hybrid roles paying $100K+, curated and updated daily. AI Auto Apply relies on external job boards you must configure separately.</p>
      <p><strong>User pain solved:</strong> Scattered job search across multiple sites → <strong>Outcome:</strong> One platform for browsing, tailoring, and applying</p>

      <h3>4. Application Control and Transparency</h3>
      <p>You review every tailored resume before it's sent. You see exactly what employers receive. AI Auto Apply applies automatically in the background with limited visibility.</p>
      <p><strong>User pain solved:</strong> Worried about sending wrong information → <strong>Outcome:</strong> Full control over every application</p>

      <h3>5. Built-in Job Tracker</h3>
      <p>Track all applications, interviews, and follow-ups in one place. No spreadsheets needed. AI Auto Apply doesn't include tracking—you'd need a separate tool.</p>
      <p><strong>User pain solved:</strong> Losing track of applications → <strong>Outcome:</strong> Organized job search with clear visibility</p>
    </section>

