      <h3>Is Jobsolv really free?</h3>
      <p>Yes. Jobsolv offers a forever-free plan that includes access to the job board, resume builder, job tracker, and limited resume tailoring. You can start applying immediately without a credit card. Premium features (unlimited tailoring, auto-apply) require a paid plan.</p>

      <h3>Does AI Auto Apply tailor resumes for each job?</h3>
      <p>No. AI Auto Apply uses one generic resume for all applications. It focuses on volume rather than customization. Jobsolv tailors your resume for each job posting, matching keywords and skills from the job description.</p>

      <h3>Which tool gets more interviews?</h3>
      <p>Jobsolv typically generates higher interview rates because each application is tailored to the specific job. AI Auto Apply may send more applications, but generic resumes have lower conversion rates, especially for competitive roles.</p>

      <h3>Can I use both tools together?</h3>
      <p>Technically yes, but it's not recommended. Using both creates duplicate applications and confusion. Choose based on your priority: quality (Jobsolv) or maximum volume (AI Auto Apply).</p>

